<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>count() method returns overall number of documents including deleted documents.</p>

<p>So it's possible to get real number of documents only after full index optimization.
It's necessary to have method for retrieving number of non-deleted documents.</p>

<p><a href="http://framework.zend.com/wiki/display/ZFMLGEN/mail/19140">FW-General discussion</a></p>

